      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GELSOMINO AMAL (1) has not raced for six months. Looks forward enough for this return after winning in a recent trial. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run and is sure to be right there at the finish. LUZIA (9) scored by 2.25 metres at Northam over 2190m last start at his first run back from a spell. May just need a bit of luck at some point from this difficult draw. Won't find this any harder and he can go right on with the job. OUR SERAPHINA (7) is heading the right way, improving last time out to finish second at this track over 2242m. Genuine threat. PURA VIDA (2) is the next elect off a last-start win by a neck at Albany over 1832m. Include from the favourable draw.",
